WWII: Operation Phoenix | Full 2025 Action Movie | Action War WW2 Movie

When the enemy capture a female spy with critical information for the Allies, a daring plan is devised to rescue her: a small group of Allied commandos will partner with a small French resistance and escapees from one of the most dreaded POW camps.  Together, they will defy the odds and bring the fight on multiple fronts, but soon realize that this battle is only just beginning.

2024.  Stars: Costas Mandylor, Suzy Alden, Richard Lyntton
